{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Bv_values.Eval</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"soteria","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Soteria","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Bv_values","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Eval","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Make\"><a href=\"#module-Make\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Make/index.html\">Make</a></span><span> (<a href=\"Make/argument-1-Ext/index.html\">Ext</a> : <a href=\"../Svalue/module-type-Value_ext/index.html\">Svalue.Value_ext</a>) (<a href=\"Make/argument-2-V/index.html\">V</a> : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span>) : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Normalisation of svalues over a <em>built</em> <code>Svalue</code> module <code>V</code> (the result of <a href=\"../Svalue/Make/index.html\"><code>Svalue.Make</code></a>). <a href=\"Make/index.html#val-eval\" title=\"Make.eval\"><code>eval</code></a> walks a value bottom-up and re-applies the simplifying smart constructors, which both simplifies and rebuilds any value that was assembled directly from raw nodes (e.g. read back from a cache).</p></div></div>"}